I also have ideas for some other cute hooded bird plushie stretch goals.

node.text:
Meet Soy!
The non-profit charity plush 🐧
(Link in bio)
Full story:
My recently turned 6yo daughter had her first experience with the real world when she found out her favourite birds are endangered.
Then she learnt that she can help.
After the initial "mummy give all your money to the penguins now! Quickly!"
She decided to create Soy with the intention to (with my help) make her into a plush toy to sell to raise money for charity. Soy, a cute baby emperor penguin, who loves her parents so much, she wears a hat that looks like them.
The plush she designed will be crowdfunded for manufacturing costs and have all profits donated to @wwf @wwf_uk to help save the penguins and contribute towards climate crisis.
.
Her Kickstarter link is in my bio
.
.
.
